metadata.name: Panel 1 Actual
metadata.description:
"What is it?" she asked.

The woman replied, "The correct question is rather, what could it be?"

They both stood gazing at the object twisting and swirling in mid air. It changed form every split second, as if it were considering thousands of possibilities for its existence.
